,"text":"Or Vision —a tearing down of a wall, or Vision —Kir raged; Hb obscure"},{"kind":"text","text":" and crying to the mountains;"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 10:6","book":"Isa","chapter":10,"verse":6},{"label":"Is 37:3","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":3},{"label":"Is 63:3","book":"Isa","chapter":63,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or Vision —a tearing down of a wall, or Vision —Kir raged; Hb obscure"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Elam took up a quiver"},{"kind":"text","text":" with chariots and horsemen, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit chariots of man"},{"kind":"text","text":" and Kir "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 16:9","book":"2Ki","chapter":16,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Am 1:5","book":"Amo","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Am 9:7","book":"Amo","chapter":9,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" uncovered the shield."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 16:9","book":"2Ki","chapter":16,"verse":9},{"label":"Am 1:5","book":"Amo","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"Am 9:7","book":"Amo","chapter":9,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit chariots of man"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Your best valleys were full of chariots,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and horsemen were positioned at the city gates."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He removed the defenses of Judah."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You saw that there were many breaches in the walls of the city of David. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 2:4","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" You collected water from the lower pool. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 20:20","book":"2Ki","chapter":20,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 3:16","book":"Neh","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 2:4","book":"Luk","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"2Kg 20:20","book":"2Ki","chapter":20,"verse":20},{"label":"Neh 3:16","book":"Neh","chapter":3,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You counted the houses of Jerusalem so that you could tear them down to fortify the wall. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You made a reservoir between the walls "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 25:4","book":"2Ki","chapter":25,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 39:4","book":"Jer","chapter":39,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the water of the ancient pool, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 20:20","book":"2Ki","chapter":20,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 32:3–4","book":"2Ch","chapter":32,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" but you did not look to the one who made it, or consider the one who created it long ago."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 25:4","book":"2Ki","chapter":25,"verse":4},{"label":"Jr 39:4","book":"Jer","chapter":39,"verse":4},{"label":"2Kg 20:20","book":"2Ki","chapter":20,"verse":20},{"label":"2Ch 32:3–4","book":"2Ch","chapter":32,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On that day the Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies"},{"kind":"text","text":" called for weeping, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 32:11","book":"Isa","chapter":32,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jl 1:13","book":"Jol","chapter":1,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jl 2:17","book":"Jol","chapter":2,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" for wailing, for shaven heads,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and for the wearing of sackcloth."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 32:11","book":"Isa","chapter":32,"verse":11},{"label":"Jl 1:13","book":"Jol","chapter":1,"verse":13},{"label":"Jl 2:17","book":"Jol","chapter":2,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But look: joy and gladness,"},{"kind":"text","text":" butchering of cattle, slaughtering of sheep and goats,"},{"kind":"text","text":" eating of meat, and drinking of wine —"},{"kind":"text","text":" “Let’s eat and drink, for tomorrow we die!” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 56:12","book":"Isa","chapter":56,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:32","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":32,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 56:12","book":"Isa","chapter":56,"verse":12},{"label":"1Co 15:32","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":32}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies has directly revealed to me: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 5:9","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" “This iniquity will not be wiped out for you people as long as you live.” "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit for you until you die"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 3:14","book":"1Sa","chapter":3,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 24:13","book":"Ezk","chapter":24,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" The Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies has spoken."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 5:9","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":9},{"label":"1Sm 3:14","book":"1Sa","chapter":3,"verse":14},{"label":"Ezk 24:13","book":"Ezk","chapter":24,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit for you until you die"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies said, “Go to Shebna, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 18:18","book":"2Ki","chapter":18,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 18:26","book":"2Ki","chapter":18,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 18:37","book":"2Ki","chapter":18,"verse":37,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 36:3","book":"Isa","chapter":36,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 36:11","book":"Isa","chapter":36,"verse":11,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 36:22","book":"Isa","chapter":36,"verse":22,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 37:2","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":2,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" that steward who is in charge of the palace, and say to him: "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 18:18","book":"2Ki","chapter":18,"verse":18},{"label":"2Kg 18:26","book":"2Ki","chapter":18,"verse":26},{"label":"2Kg 18:37","book":"2Ki","chapter":18,"verse":37},{"label":"Is 36:3","book":"Isa","chapter":36,"verse":3},{"label":"Is 36:11","book":"Isa","chapter":36,"verse":11},{"label":"Is 36:22","book":"Isa","chapter":36,"verse":22},{"label":"Is 37:2","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"What are you doing here? Who authorized you to carve out a tomb for yourself here, carving your tomb on the height and cutting a resting place for yourself out of rock? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 18:18","book":"2Sa","chapter":18,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 16:14","book":"2Ch","chapter":16,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 27:60","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":60,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Sm 18:18","book":"2Sa","chapter":18,"verse":18},{"label":"2Ch 16:14","book":"2Ch","chapter":16,"verse":14},{"label":"Mt 27:60","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":60}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Look, you strong man! The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" is about to shake you violently. He will take hold of you, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"wind you up into a ball, and sling you into a wide land. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"},{"kind":"text","text":" There you will die, and there your glorious chariots will be —a disgrace to the house of your lord. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will remove you from your office; you will be ousted from your position."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“On that day I will call for my servant, Eliakim son of Hilkiah. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 18:18","book":"2Ki","chapter":18,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 36:3","book":"Isa","chapter":36,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 36:22","book":"Isa","chapter":36,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 37:2","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":2,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 18:18","book":"2Ki","chapter":18,"verse":18},{"label":"Is 36:3","book":"Isa","chapter":36,"verse":3},{"label":"Is 36:22","book":"Isa","chapter":36,"verse":22},{"label":"Is 37:2","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will clothe him with your robe and tie your sash around him. I will hand your authority over to him, and he will be like a father to the inhabitants of Jerusalem and to the house of Judah. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 45:8","book":"Gen","chapter":45,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 29:16","book":"Job","chapter":29,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 45:8","book":"Gen","chapter":45,"verse":8},{"label":"Jb 29:16","book":"Job","chapter":29,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will place the key "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 16:19","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 3:7","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" of the house of David on his shoulder; what he opens, no one can close; what he closes, no one can open. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 12:14","book":"Job","chapter":12,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 16:19","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":19},{"label":"Rv 3:7","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":7},{"label":"Jb 12:14","book":"Job","chapter":12,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will drive him, like a peg, into a firm place. He will be a throne of honor for his father’s family. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They will hang on him all the glory of his father’s family: the descendants and the offshoots —all the small vessels, from bowls to every kind of jar. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:22:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On that day” —the declaration of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies —“the peg that was driven into a firm place will give way, be cut off, and fall, and the load on it will be destroyed.” Indeed, the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" has spoken."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279543652}